#: ../../source/guides/account/creating-and-opening-an-account.rst:43
msgid ""
"The **private key** uniquely identifies a NEM account and holds all of "
"its power. It is a priority to make sure it is stored safely somewhere "
"**offline** and not to share it with anyone."
msgstr "**私钥**使NEM账户相互区别并多账户享有控制权。确保私钥安全地存储在 **离线** 的某个地方，而不是与任何人共享它，这是一个需要注意的事项。"

#: ../../source/guides/account/creating-and-opening-an-account.rst:45
msgid ""
"The **public key** is cryptographically derived from the private key and "
"safe to be shared. In spite of that, it is preferable to share the "
"**address**, which contains further information such as network and "
"validity check."
msgstr "**公钥**是从私钥加密派生的，可以安全地共享。尽管如此，还是最好共享 **地址**，其中包含更多信息，如网络和有效性检查。"

